fundamental point of an enzyme,

00:46:31.410 --> 00:46:35.090
which is that they,
especially enzymes in biology,

00:46:35.090 --> 00:46:39.690
can be exquisitely specific.

00:46:39.690 --> 00:46:43.420
What you're saying
is that it's really

00:46:43.420 --> 00:46:46.010
