00:54:12.570 --> 00:54:15.370
at saturation, when you
have a lot of the substrate.

00:54:34.460 --> 00:54:36.290
Do you need time?

00:54:36.290 --> 00:54:39.489
Or will time help?

00:54:39.489 --> 00:54:40.530
